cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SD

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on natural language understanding and translation for conversational systems. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is also a likely category as the paper deals with building keyword-based queries for search-oriented conversational systems. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper proposes a reinforcement-learning-driven translation model framework. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the paper uses machine learning techniques for the translation model. 
- cs.SD (Sound) is a less likely category as there is no mention of sound or audio in the paper.
